        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44747017/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44747017/" class="">第15页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/57611591/" class=" " title="willfina">willfina</a>
              
                <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="44747017">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">八阿哥九阿哥被抄家，他們之間的通信都是用的拉丁文這句，說的應該就是被改名成塞思黑阿其那那兩個阿哥吧？人家是皈依了基督教才學的拉丁文，也是怕別人看懂他們的書信這兩個原因，你居然說人家洋氣，跟歐洲宮廷差不多。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-06-09 19:33</span>
                  
